{"tid":1766791,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"央視：被割頸警員對獨立調查委員會持開放態度","createTime":"2019-12-03T00:44:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T03:42:41.000Z","uid":71954,"like":7,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"51e9400fb5d1de9ade3f85a2a38ff1e4f8bddd7f","tid":1766791,"uid":71954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T00:44:27.000Z","msg":"一名警員10月處理刑事毀壞案件時，被人用利器割頸受傷。他日前接受中央電視台訪問，強調面對暴徒致命的暴力襲擊，警員只是使用低層次的武力。<br />\n<br />\n遭割頸警員稱︰「警察用多少程度的武力，是視乎他受到甚麼武力的襲擊。我不認同警察用了過大的武力去處理這個事件。雖然我受了傷，但我在電視見到有人用汽油彈、掟磚、用箭襲擊我的同事，這全部是致命的暴力襲擊。而警察所使用的都是相對來說較低層次的武力去處理這個事件。」<br />\n<br />\n該警員表示，他受傷當日做了四個小時手術，醫生指他靜脈及迷走神經被割斷，幸好沒有傷及動脈。<br />\n<br />\n他指警察只是執法者，不涉及任何的政治爭執，有人犯法便應該處理，批評香港有一部分人完全沒有獨立思維，被別人影響去做一些激進的行為。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">對於設立獨立調查委員會，他持開放態度</span>，但認為大學校長及受過高等教育的人都針對警察和政府，不知該找甚麼人擔任委員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/5de5536ae60383c10237b91d/%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%A9%E5%99%A8%E5%89%B2%E9%A0%B8%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E8%A8%AA%E5%95%8F-%E6%8C%87%E5%B0%8D%E8%87%B4%E5%91%BD%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E5%8F%AA%E7%94%A8%E4%BD%8E%E5%B1%A4%E6%AC%A1%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fgreaterchina%2F5de5536ae60383c10237b91d%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%2599%25A8%25E5%2589%25B2%25E9%25A0%25B8%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E5%2595%258F-%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%2587%25B4%25E5%2591%25BD%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A%25E5%258F%25AA%25E7%2594%25A8%25E4%25BD%258E%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%258A%259B&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRaix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=cb7c390f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/5de5536ae60383c10237b91d/%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%A9%E5%99%A8%E5%89%B2%E9%A0%B8%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E8%A8%AA%E5%95%8F-%E6%8C%87%E5%B0%8D%E8%87%B4%E5%91%BD%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E5%8F%AA%E7%94%A8%E4%BD%8E%E5%B1%A4%E6%AC%A1%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B</a>"},{"pid":"baa06e3c4333a75c4f61e8e7d1e6c07db78e4c7b","tid":1766791,"uid":84128,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T00:45:41.000Z","msg":"但認為大學校長及受過高等教育的人都針對警察和政府，不知該找甚麼人擔任委員。<br />\n<br />\n認下點解啦屌你老母<br />\n實係班書都無讀過既人勁過讀得書架啦"},{"pid":"6347098d61d5b80a600b317f21b4c25749ba9c48","tid":1766791,"uid":289021,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T00:45:54.000Z","msg":"俾人割完頸淆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66026feea412066e58fc2a0063a798fcda66ba3","tid":1766791,"uid":6810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"baa06e3c4333a75c4f61e8e7d1e6c07db78e4c7b","tid":1766791,"uid":84128,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T00:45:41.000Z","msg":"但認為大學校長及受過高等教育的人都針對警察和政府，不知該找甚麼人擔任委員。<br />\n<br />\n認下點解啦屌你老母<br />\n實係班書都無讀過既人勁過讀得書架啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T00:47:26.000Z","msg":"搵林大總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ab40add84231deb47a379c04e08f1a6b140e28","tid":1766791,"uid":203713,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T00:48:32.000Z","msg":"佢地真係以為自己啱先好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9051e04cf5ae7c916c8cd028e5a9ab567f13b74a","tid":1766791,"uid":71954,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T00:50:45.000Z","msg":"央視咁播出街即係吹緊風成立獨立調查委員會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭搞獨立 &ldquo;檢討&rdquo; 委員會即係唔聽中央話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb13c9ee3ee89f9c73a90a2c854eda3aea1a1012","tid":1766791,"uid":236368,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T00:51:06.000Z","msg":"cctv報得即係強國唔反對設調查委員會，但最後可能求其推幾個人出嚟死就算"},{"pid":"ed7f99cb38666aee028212f9118d3018ea9d21ac","tid":1766791,"uid":71954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb13c9ee3ee89f9c73a90a2c854